<h1 style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #111827;">Delivery Confirmed!</h1>
<p style="margin: 0 0 24px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  Hey <%= @user.name %>, your delivery is all set. Here are your details:
</p>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #d1fae5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px;">
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
          <td width="50%" style="padding: 8px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 2px; font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Date</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #111827; font-weight: 700;"><%= @appointment.scheduled_date.strftime('%A, %B %d, %Y') %></p>
          </td>
          <td width="50%" style="padding: 8px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 2px; font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Time</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #111827; font-weight: 700;"><%= @appointment.scheduled_time.strftime('%I:%M %p') %></p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2" style="padding: 8px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 2px; font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Confirmation #</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #111827; font-weight: 700;">CRV-<%= @appointment.id.to_s.rjust(6, '0') %></p>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;">What to have ready:</h3>
<ul style="margin: 0 0 24px; padding-left: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;">
  <li>Valid driver's license (matching your uploaded ID)</li>
  <li>Proof of insurance (active coverage)</li>
  <li>Be at your delivery address during the time window</li>
</ul>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color: #e0f7fc; padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 12px;">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #0090b3;">
        <strong>Remember:</strong> You have 7 days and 400 miles to make sure you love your car. If not, return it free.
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
